han pole vault star EJ Obiena.\", \"from\": 233, \"to\": 435, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 233, \"end\": 238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Dylan\", \"score\": 0.999999994548034, \"rank\": 5.451952724199666e-09, \"text\": \"Dylan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Dylan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Dylan\"}, {\"begin\": 239, \"end\": 247, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isaiah_Martinez\", \"score\": 0.9962910735786691, \"rank\": 0.0037227337317798934, \"text\": \"Martinez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isaiah_Martinez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isaiah_Martinez\"}, {\"begin\": 248, \"end\": 255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"REUTERS\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}, {\"begin\": 265, \"end\": 276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.471761390426572e-15, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 356, \"end\": 392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippine_Sportswriters_Association_Annual_Awards\", \"score\": 0.9999996688539434, \"rank\": 3.3114636600264353e-07, \"text\": \"Philippine Sportswriters Association\", \"types\": [\"Q618779\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippine_Sportswriters_Association_Annual_Awards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippine_Sportswriters_Association_Annual_Awards\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"No other Filipino\", \"from\": 278, \"to\": 295}, {\"ngram\": \"the Athlete\", \"from\": 316, \"to\": 327}, {\"ngram\": \"the Year\", \"from\": 331, \"to\": 339}, {\"ngram\": \"award\", \"from\": 340, \"to\": 345}, {\"ngram\": \"(PSA\", \"from\": 392, \"to\": 396}, {\"ngram\": \"pole vault star\", \"from\": 408, \"to\": 423}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Obiena earned the highest individual honor from the Philippines' oldest media organization during the PSA Awards Nights on Monday, January 29, following a banner year that has put him in medal conversation for the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 437, \"to\": 666, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 489, \"end\": 500, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.471761390426572e-15, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines_men's_national_basketball_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Obiena\", \"from\": 437, \"to\": 443}, {\"ngram\": \"the highest individual honor\", \"from\": 451, \"to\": 479}, {\"ngram\": \"the PSA Awards Nights\", \"from\": 535, \"to\": 556}, {\"ngram\": \"Monday\", \"from\": 560, \"to\": 566}, {\"ngram\": \"January\", \"from\": 568, \"to\": 575}, {\"ngram\": \"a banner year\", \"from\": 590, \"to\": 603}, {\"ngram\": \"medal conversation\", \"from\": 624, \"to\": 642}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 647, \"to\": 665}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On a mission not just to bring honor to the country but also inspire the next generation, Obiena - who appeared virtually at the Diamond Hotel as he remains in Italy for training - said the award means he is on the right path.\", \"from\": 668, \"to\": 894, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 828, \"end\": 833, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.6548245609064949, \"rank\": 0.35675389611007285, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a mission\", \"from\": 671, \"to\": 680}, {\"ngram\": \"honor\", \"from\": 699, \"to\": 704}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 708, \"to\": 719}, {\"ngram\": \"the next generation\", \"from\": 737, \"to\": 756}, {\"ngram\": \"Obiena\", \"from\": 758, \"to\": 764}, {\"ngram\": \"the Diamond Hotel\", \"from\": 793, \"to\": 810}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 838, \"to\": 846}, {\"ngram\": \"the award\", \"from\": 854, \"to\": 863}, {\"ngram\": \"the right path\", \"from\": 879, \"to\": 893}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I stand here, truly humbled by this award, arguably the most prestigious award any Filipino athlete can get, an award I have dreamed way back in 2017, my first PSA [Awards] Night,\\\" he said through a Zoom call.\", \"from\": 896, \"to\": 1106, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this award\", \"from\": 928, \"to\": 938}, {\"ngram\": \"any Filipino athlete\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 996}, {\"ngram\": \"my first PSA\", \"from\": 1048, \"to\": 1060}, {\"ngram\": \"a Zoom call\", \"from\": 1094, \"to\": 1105}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This award suggest perhaps, in some degree, I have been successful in the mission, not in pole vaulting, but in leveraging my craft to help shape a better Philippines, and I would say, a stronger Philippines.\\\"\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1318, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1264, \"end\": 1275, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.471761390426572e-15, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1305, \"end\": 1316, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.471761390426572e-15, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines_men's_national_basketball_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This award\", \"from\": 1109, \"to\": 1119}, {\"ngram\": \"some degree\", \"from\": 1140, \"to\": 1151}, {\"ngram\": \"the mission\", \"from\": 1179, \"to\": 1190}, {\"ngram\": \"pole vaulting\", \"from\": 1199, \"to\": 1212}, {\"ngram\": \"my craft\", \"from\": 1232, \"to\": 1240}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ranked second in the world, Obiena reached greater heights last year as he became the first Asian to clear the six-meter barrier, joining an elite club composed of only 27 other pole vaulters.\", \"from\": 1320, \"to\": 1512, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1412, \"end\": 1417, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0053849002380588e-17, \"text\": \"Asian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1337, \"to\": 1346}, {\"ngram\": \"Obiena\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1354}, {\"ngram\": \"greater heights\", \"from\": 1363, \"to\": 1378}, {\"ngram\": \"the six-meter barrier\", \"from\": 1427, \"to\": 1448}, {\"ngram\": \"an elite club\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1471}, {\"ngram\": \"only 27 other pole vaulters\", \"from\": 1484, \"to\": 1511}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 28-year-old achieved the feat when he ruled theBergen Jump Challengein Norway in June as he improved his own Asian record.\", \"from\": 1514, \"to\": 1640, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the feat\", \"from\": 1539, \"to\": 1547}, {\"ngram\": \"theBergen Jump Challengein Norway\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1595}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 1599, \"to\": 1603}, {\"ngram\": \"his own Asian record\", \"from\": 1619, \"to\": 1639}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, Obiena did it twice last year as he recorded six meters anew to bag a historic silver in theWorld Athletics Championshipin Hungary in August, placing behind world record holder Armand Duplantis of Sweden.\", \"from\": 1642, \"to\": 1855, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1774, \"end\": 1781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9977612077795828, \"rank\": 0.0022438156028390982, \"text\": \"Hungary\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1828, \"end\": 1844, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armand_Duplantis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Armand Duplantis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armand_Duplantis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armand_Duplantis\"}, {\"begin\": 1848, \"end\": 1854, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9490291716941568, \"rank\": 0.052576733541214705, \"text\": \"Sweden\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden_women's_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 1645, \"to\": 1649}, {\"ngram\": \"Obiena\", \"from\": 1651, \"to\": 1657}, {\"ngram\": \"a historic silver\", \"from\": 1719, \"to\": 1736}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 1785, \"to\": 1791}, {\"ngram\": \"world record holder\", \"from\": 1808, \"to\": 1827}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That silver reset the Philippines' highest finish in the World Athletics Championships, a distinction Obiena also owned when he clinched bronze in the 2022 edition.\", \